Content.Text:
<FACE_WITCH><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
W-What was that? You just say that
again!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
Oh dear, are you going deaf? I'll
accommodate you then, my dear, by 
repeating myself. You are a simpleton!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Enough! I'm not going to take any more
of this slander from you, you airhead!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Hey, <MYNAME>! Get out of my way!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
She's right, <MYNAME>. Move aside. It's
time for this witch to be put firmly in
her place!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
What are you talking about? That's my
line! You'll be begging me to stop
before I'm done with you!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
N-Not bad, for a Harvest Goddess!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
Buttering me up won't get you anywhere.
My next spell will finish you!

<FACE_GODDES><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
W-What's going on? There's... two of me?

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
Haah, haah, haah... Swapping bodies with
the Goddess... what a terrifying
experience!
<PAGE>
I'm glad I finally returned to normal.
If I had been stuck like that... I don't
even want to think of it!

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
I know. I should have stopped when you
tried to step in, <MYNAME>.
<PAGE>
I've learnt my lesson, at least for a
short while. I won't attack her again.
Not just yet.
<PAGE>
She took some damage too, from the look
of it.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_LOSS>
I'm going to be bored for a while.

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ROUGH>
How about helping me out with an
experiment or two, then?

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_NORMAL>
Come now, <MYNAME>. Will you help me out a
little?

<FACE_WITCH><POS_LEFT><FACE_ANGRY>
I just wanted to clear my head! You need
to stop playing hard to get.
